          Workers' compensation coverage tailored to the Capital Region's government and professional economy
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Government Contractors -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Government Contractors</h3>
